<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<title>Insert title here</title>
<link rel="stylesheet" href="../css/public.css">
<script src="../js/jquery-3.5.1.min.js"></script>

<style>
</style>

<script>
$(function(){
   $('.box1 > input:button').on('click', function(){
      
      //각 요소의 상태값 가져오기
      a = $('#checkTest').prop("checked");
      b = $('#selTest>option').eq(0).prop('selected');
      c = $('#txtTest').prop('readonly');
      d = $('#runBtn').prop('disabled');
      
      res = "체크박스 checked : " + a + "<br>";
      res += "select option : " + b + "<br>";
      res += "text readonly : " + c + "<br>";
      res += "button disabled : " + d + "<br>";

      $('#result1 div').html(res);	
   })
})
</script>

</head>
<body>
	<div class="box box1">
		각 요소의 상태값을 얻는다<br>
		- true 또는 false를 리턴한다.<br>
		- prop(상태속성)  - $(this).prop('readonly');<br>
		
		상태속성으로 사용하는 것 : readonly, disabled, checked, selected, multiple<br>
		
		
		<br> <br> <input type="button" value="확인" onclick="proc1()">

		<div id="result1">

			<form>
				체크박스(라디오버튼) : 
				<input type="checkbox" id="checkTest" checked><br>
				<br> 리스트박스(select객체) : 
				<select id="selTest">
					<option value="1">하나</option>
					<option value="2">둘</option>
					<option value="3" selected>셋</option>
					<option value="4">넷</option>
				</select><br> 
				text객체 (readonly) : 
				<input readonly="readonly" type="text" value="가나다" id="txtTest"><br> <br>
				button객체(disabled) : 
				<input disabled="disabled" type="button" onclick="alert('Hello')" value="실행" id="runBtn">
			</form>
			<div></div>

		</div>
	</div>
</body>
</html>